s to the case\nof a random two-dimensional pinning landscape, we discuss the topological\nproperties of unstable and bistable regions as expressed through the Euler\ncharacteristic, with the latter related to the local differential properties of\n$D(\\mathbf{R})$ through Morse theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jan 2023 19:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-09"}
