s/accretion events, and that three out of\nfour inner halo stars have prograde orbits. Large spectroscopic surveys may\ncontain many hidden extremely and ultra metal-poor stars, and adding additional\ninformation from e.g. photometry as in this work can uncover them more\nefficiently and confidently.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jan 2023 19:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
