ncides with the existing result for a random walk in the\nquarter plane without background processes, obtained by Malyshev (Siberian\nMath. J., vol. 12, ,pp. 109-118, 1973).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 09:38:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Feb 2023 00:26:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
