to existing MU-MIMO schemes on OTFS and orthogonal frequency-division\nmultiplexing (OFDM).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 10:32:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2023 07:12:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-31"}
